<div id="review_380077839" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/380077839" />
    <a title="Ellinor" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8307014-ellinor"><img alt="Ellinor" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1573658130p2/8307014.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/380077839?book_show_action=true">Nov 28, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ellinor" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ellinor" href="/user/show/8307014-ellinor">Ellinor</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780374520571" href="/book/show/6329609-the-enchanted-wanderer">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8307014-ellinor?shelf=1001-books">1001-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8307014-ellinor?shelf=short-stories">short-stories</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8307014-ellinor?shelf=1001-books-2006">1001-books-2006</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8307014-ellinor?shelf=1001-books-core-list">1001-books-core-list</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer380077839" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8496106968397422858">This selection of tales is not what you&apos;re excepting from a Russian writer. Especially the title giving tale The Enchanted Wanderer is very entertaining. It is a classic picaresque tale and reminded me a lot of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19380.Candide' title='Candide by Voltaire' rel='nofollow noopener'>Candide</a>.<br/>The story I enjoyed most was Lady Macbeth of Mtsensk. The main character kills both her father in law and her husband to live with her lover. I didn&apos;t judge her for that but later for mudering the child and I liked her revenge at the end of the tale.</span>
  <span id="freeText8496106968397422858" style="display:none">This selection of tales is not what you're excepting from a Russian writer. Especially the title giving tale The Enchanted Wanderer is very entertaining. It is a classic picaresque tale and reminded me a lot of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19380.Candide" title="Candide by Voltaire" rel="nofollow noopener">Candide</a>.<br />The story I enjoyed most was Lady Macbeth of Mtsensk. The main character kills both her father in law and her husband to live with her lover. I didn't judge her for that but later for mudering the child and I liked her revenge at the end of the tale.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8496106968397422858" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


