      var newTip = new Tip($('bookCover_229733'), "\n\n  <h2><a class=\"readable bookTitle\" href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/229733.The_White_Guard?from_choice=false&amp;from_home_module=false\">The White Guard<\/a><\/h2>\n\n      <div>\n        by <a class=\"authorName\" href=\"/author/show/3873.Mikhail_Bulgakov?a=9&amp;origin=related_works\">Mikhail Bulgakov<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n\n          <div class=\"smallText uitext darkGreyText\">\n            <span class=\"minirating\"><span class=\"stars staticStars notranslate\"><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p3\"><\/span><\/span> 4.04 avg rating &mdash; 11,994 ratings<\/span>            &mdash; published 1925\n          <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"addBookTipDescription\">\n      \n<span id=\"freeTextContainer506972410807062704\">Although less famous than Mikhail Bulgakov&apos;s comic hit, The Master and Margarita, The White Guard is still an engrossing book, though completely different in tone. It is set in Kiev during the Russian revolution and tells the story of the Turbin fami<\/span>\n  <span id=\"freeText506972410807062704\" style=\"display:none\">Although less famous than Mikhail Bulgakov\'s comic hit, The Master and Margarita, The White Guard is still an engrossing book, though completely different in tone. It is set in Kiev during the Russian revolution and tells the story of the Turbin family and the war\'s effect on the middle-classes (not workers). \n\nThe story was not seen as politically correct, and thereby contributed to Bulgakov\'s lifelong troubles with the Soviet authorities. It was, however, a well-loved book, and the novel was turned into a successful play at the time of its publication in 1967.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"506972410807062704\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapC